ABUJA – All Progressives Congress APC national Chairmanship Aspirant, Salisu Mustapha has enjoined members of the party to renew their hope in ability of the APC to fulfill it’s promise to Nigeria. In a new year message to APC faithful the Turaki of Ilorin said the new year present opportunity for abundant possibilities the party offers. He Insists that members must work hard to sustain the gains and fundamental ideal of the APC as a Progressive party. Says Ortom Had No Hand In Selection Of Ochi’Idoma -CPS 2023: APC Working On One Lie That Will Return PDP To Power… Mustapha said: “Anew year is always the beginning of a new journey, a chance to make amends where necessary and to start again on a different trajectory. “Our party, APC, has come a long way and recorded significant milestones, but we are now on the threshold of another history, as we prepare for the party’s National Convention. This requires us to reflect on our journey so far and our future as progressives. “As we begin another year, the task of working to sustain the gains of the APC as a party and the government it birthed has become even much more significant. “As a true party man, I’m aware of the aspirat’ons of majority of APC members to sustain the fundamental ideals of the party, and to continue to bequeath to Nigerians progressive governance that elevate the fortunes of our dear country. “While welcoming you all, fellow party men and women, to the year 2022, | implore you to open your minds to the abundant possibilities entrenched in the vision and mandate of APC; and to renew your belief that our best days as a party are just beginning “.